      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELITE ARNOTT (1) pinged the lids from a wide box and crossed to the lead, sticking on for second (22.08) at this track in a Novice race over 381m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Makes plenty of appeal. ROXY KEEPING (5) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish half a length back in second (22.22) at this track in a Novice race over 381m. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Will give a great sight again. ORANA JET (4) was a last-start winner from the rails at this track and distance (22.19) after forging to the front and leading throughout, scoring by half a length. Leading player again. CLOUD KEEPING (2) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
